          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Tout l'Essentiel +</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> SIEM 24/7 + alertes temps réel</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Dashboard client Live SOC</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Support prioritaire (4h)</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Pen-test annuel inclus</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact?run=pro" class="btn btn-primary">S'abonner</a>
